rows.label: qev015203_MSG0003
rows.name:
So this project to build a water-purification plant in
Primordia is moving forward.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015203_MSG0004
rows.name:
That is, when we're not being attacked by indigens
or running out of building materials. Ugh!
What a nightmare![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015203_MSG0005
rows.name:
I TOLD them building anything in a place like that was
crazypants! Don't know why they didn't listen...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015203_MSG0001
rows.name:
Huh. Well, it looks like construction is back on track
for the water-purification plant. ...FINALLY![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015203_MSG0002
rows.name:
Stupid Ajoa was gloating like she solved everything.
Ugh, I just want to smack her![ST:wait ]
